  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, bring the beef broth to a boil over high heat.",
    "Add the ginger and cayenne pepper to the pot and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "In a blender, combine the soy sauce, sugar, citrus juice, and a pinch of salt and pepper. Blend until smooth.",
    "Using a slotted spoon, remove the ginger and cayenne pepper from the pot and discard.",
    "Strain the broth through a fine-mesh sieve into a clean pot, discarding any solids.",
    "Add the blanch and rice noodles to the pot and cook for 3-5 minutes, or until the noodles are tender.",
    "Stir in the cheddar cheese until melted and smooth.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning with fish sauce, soy sauce, sugar, and citrus juice as needed.",
    "Garnish with scallions, cilantro, and a sprinkle of salt and pepper.",
    "Serve hot, immediately."
  ],
